data.yamlPipeline:
pipeline:
    stages:
        - stage:
              name: appd
              identifier: appd
              description: ""
              type: Deployment
              spec:
                  serviceConfig:
                      serviceRef: <+input>
                      serviceDefinition:
                          type: Kubernetes
                          spec:
                              variables: []
                  infrastructure:
                      environmentRef: re
                      infrastructureDefinition:
                          type: KubernetesDirect
                          spec:
                              connectorRef: dynatrace
                              namespace: default1
                              releaseName: release-<+INFRA_KEY>
                      allowSimultaneousDeployments: false
                  execution:
                      steps:
                          - step:
                                name: Rollout Deployment
                                identifier: rolloutDeployment
                                type: K8sRollingDeploy
                                timeout: 10m
                                spec:
                                    skipDryRun: false
                          - step:
                                type: ShellScript
                                name: Shell Script
                                identifier: Shell_Script
                                spec:
                                    shell: Bash
                                    onDelegate: true
                                    source:
                                        type: Inline
                                        spec:
                                            script: echo 1
                                    environmentVariables: []
                                    outputVariables: []
                                    executionTarget: {}
                                timeout: 10m
                      rollbackSteps:
                          - step:
                                name: Rollback Rollout Deployment
                                identifier: rollbackRolloutDeployment
                                type: K8sRollingRollback
                                timeout: 10m
                                spec: {}
                  serviceDependencies: []
              tags: {}
              failureStrategies:
                  - onFailure:
                        errors:
                            - AllErrors
                        action:
                            type: StageRollback
    name: appd_test
    identifier: appd_test
    tags: {}
    projectIdentifier: project1
    orgIdentifier: default
